    This overview has introduced the fundamental vocabulary, architectural concepts, and operational metrics of modern ecommerce. As the field continues evolving—with AI personalization, AR/VR shopping experiences, and social commerce reshaping customer expectations—maintaining current technical knowledge is essential for competitive success.
  </p>

